---
export const prerender = true;

import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy | GG-Gels';
const description =
  'How GG-Gels processes personal data from the waitlist in compliance with the GDPR and Norwegian data protection law.';

const lastUpdated = '22 April 2026';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="bg-parchment text-ink">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-28">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <p class="text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-ink/60 mb-3">Privacy</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-ink/60 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-ink max-w-none space-y-10 leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <p>
            This privacy policy describes how GG-Gels collects and processes personal data
            from people who sign up to the waitlist on gg-gels.no. We process personal data
            in accordance with the Norwegian Personal Data Act and the EU General Data
            Protection Regulation (GDPR).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">1. Data controller</h2>
          <p>
            The data controller is Markus Remmen as a private individual. GG-Gels is a
            project name pending incorporation.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Name: Markus Remmen</li>
            <li>Address: Oslo, Norway</li>
            <li>Contact: <a class="underline" href="mailto:hei@gg-gels.no">hei@gg-gels.no</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">2. What data we process</h2>
          <p>When you sign up to the waitlist, we store the following data:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Email address (required)</li>
            <li>Handicap level</li>
            <li>How often you play golf</li>
            <li>Whether you currently use sports gels or nutrition during your round</li>
            <li>What matters to you when picking a sports gel</li>
            <li>What you would be willing to pay for a 4-pack</li>
            <li>How you heard about GG-Gels</li>
            <li>Which golf club you play at (optional)</li>
            <li>Timestamp of your signup</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            In addition, your browser sends your IP address to Cloudflare Turnstile solely
            for bot verification at the moment the form is submitted. The IP address is not
            stored by us.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">3. Purposes and legal basis</h2>
          <p>We process your data for the following purposes:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>
              Sending you email with information about the product launch, early bird
              discount and important updates about GG-Gels.
            </li>
            <li>
              Analysing aggregate demand to validate the concept before launch (e.g.
              distribution of handicap, willingness to pay, and attribution).
            </li>
            <li>Protecting the form from abuse (bot verification via Cloudflare Turnstile).</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The legal basis for processing is your consent, cf. GDPR Article 6(1)(a). You
            may withdraw your consent at any time by unsubscribing (see section 7).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">4. Data processors</h2>
          <p>
            We use the following sub-processors to process data on our behalf under a data
            processing agreement:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
            <li>
              <strong>Supabase</strong> — database for waitlist registrations.
              <a
                class="underline"
                href="https://supabase.com/privacy"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">supabase.com/privacy</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Resend</strong> — sending confirmation and update emails.
              <a
                class="underline"
                href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">resend.com/legal/privacy-policy</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Cloudflare</strong> — website hosting and bot protection (Turnstile).
              <a
                class="underline"
                href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">cloudflare.com/privacypolicy</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">5. Transfers outside the EEA</h2>
          <p>
            Some of our processors are established in the United States (Resend,
            Cloudflare). Transfers take place on the basis of the European Commission's
            adequacy decision under the EU–US Data Privacy Framework and/or the Standard
            Contractual Clauses adopted by the Commission. The database (Supabase) runs in
            an EU region.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">6. Retention period</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your data until we either launch the product or decide not to launch
            it – at the latest until 30 June 2027. If you unsubscribe from the waitlist
            before then, your data is deleted without undue delay.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">7. Your rights</h2>
          <p>For as long as we process personal data about you, you have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-1">
            <li>Request access to the data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Request restriction of processing</li>
            <li>Object to the processing</li>
            <li>Request data portability (to receive your data in a machine-readable format)</li>
            <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You can exercise your rights by emailing
            <a class="underline" href="mailto:hei@gg-gels.no">hei@gg-gels.no</a>. We will
            respond within 30 days.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You also have the right to lodge a complaint about the processing with the
            Norwegian Data Protection Authority (Datatilsynet). See
            <a
              class="underline"
              href="https://www.datatilsynet.no/en/"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer">datatilsynet.no</a
            > for more information.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">8. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            This website currently sets <strong>no cookies</strong>. We also use no tracking
            or analytics tools that would require consent. If this changes in the future,
            you will be asked to give active consent before any such services are enabled,
            and this policy will be updated.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">9. Security</h2>
          <p>
            Data is transmitted encrypted (HTTPS/TLS) and stored behind access controls
            with our processors. Only those who need access to operate the waitlist have
            access to the data.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">10. Changes</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this policy. The current version will always be available on this
            page, and material changes will be communicated by email to people on the
            waitlist.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mb-3">11. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Questions about this policy or the processing of your data can be sent to
            <a class="underline" href="mailto:hei@gg-gels.no">hei@gg-gels.no</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-ink/10">
        <a href="/en/" class="text-sm text-ink/60 underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">
          ← Back to home
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
